---
import SectionTitle from '../common/SectionTitle.astro';
const logos = Array.from({ length: 20 }, (_, i) => `/images/marcas/marca-${String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}.jpg`);
const rowSize = Math.ceil(logos.length / 2);
const rows = [logos.slice(0, rowSize), logos.slice(rowSize)];
---
<section class="section marks" id="marcas">
  <div class="container">
    <SectionTitle eyebrow="Prova real" title="Marcas já registradas" description="Marcas que protegemos junto ao INPI — cada certificado é a garantia de exclusividade de uso por 10 anos." />
    <div class="marks-intro reveal">
      <div class="owner-frame">
        <div class="owner">
          <img src="/images/owner-certificates.jpg" alt="Titular da Registrium ao lado das marcas registradas" />
          <div class="plate">Registrium · Copyright e Marcas</div>
          <div class="owner-inset"><img src="/images/owner-portrait.jpg" alt="Registrium" /></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="marks-intro-copy">
        <div class="mi-kicker">Confiança que se vê</div>
        <h3>Cada logo abaixo é uma marca real, registrada pela Registrium junto ao INPI.</h3>
        <p>De clínicas a distribuidoras, de comércio a serviços — empresas de portes diferentes confiaram na Registrium para proteger o nome que construíram.</p>
        <div class="marks-stats">
          <div><div class="mn">95%</div><div class="ml">de aprovação pelo consumidor</div></div>
          <div><div class="mn">10 anos</div><div class="ml">de proteção por certificado</div></div>
          <div><div class="mn">100%</div><div class="ml">acompanhadas até o fim</div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="logo-marquee reveal">
      {rows.map((row, rowIndex) => (
        <div class:list={['marquee-row', { reverse: rowIndex % 2 === 1 }]}>
          <div class="marquee-track">
            {[...row, ...row].map((src) => (
              <div class="tile"><img src={src} alt="Marca registrada pela Registrium junto ao INPI" loading="lazy" /></div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <p class="marks-note">Logotipos de marcas reais registradas pela Registrium junto ao INPI, exibidos a título de portfólio.</p>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
.marks-intro { display: grid; grid-template-columns: .55fr 1.45fr; gap: 2.5rem; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 3rem; }
.owner-frame { position: relative; }
.owner-frame::before, .owner-frame::after { content: ""; position: absolute; border-radius: 999px; pointer-events: none; }
.owner-frame::before { inset: -1.25rem; border: 1px solid rgba(138,87,206,.22); }
.owner-frame::after { inset: -2.75rem; border: 1px solid rgba(63,160,222,.14); }
.owner { position: relative; z-index: 1; border-radius: var(--radius-md); overflow: hidden; background: linear-gradient(160deg, #241a52, #12123a); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); aspect-ratio: 4/5; box-shadow: 0 30px 60px -34px rgba(30,20,80,.45); }
.owner img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
.owner::after { content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(8,10,36,.55) 0%, transparent 38%); pointer-events: none; }
.owner-inset { position: absolute; left: 1.125rem; bottom: 1.125rem; width: 30%; aspect-ratio: 1/1; border-radius: .875rem; overflow: hidden; border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.9); box-shadow: 0 14px 28px -10px rgba(8,10,36,.6); z-index: 2; }
.owner-inset img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
.owner .plate { position: absolute; left: 1.125rem; top: 1.125rem; background: rgba(10,11,36,.72); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18); backdrop-filter: blur(6px); border-radius: 999px; padding: .5rem 1.125rem; font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .81rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-white); white-space: nowrap; z-index: 2; }
.marks-intro-copy .mi-kicker { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-violet); margin-bottom: .625rem; }
.marks-intro-copy h3 { font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: .75rem; line-height: 1.25; }
.marks-intro-copy p { font-size: .94rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 .875rem; }
.marks-stats { display: flex; gap: 1.75rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
.marks-stats div { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.marks-stats .mn { font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.625rem; color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1; }
.marks-stats .ml { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--color-muted); margin-top: .375rem; }
.logo-marquee { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; overflow: hidden; -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #000 6%, #000 94%, transparent); mask-image: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #000 6%, #000 94%, transparent); }
.marquee-row { overflow: hidden; }
.marquee-track { display: flex; width: max-content; gap: 1rem; animation: marquee 34s linear infinite; }
.marquee-row.reverse .marquee-track { animation-direction: reverse; animation-duration: 40s; }
.marquee-row:hover .marquee-track { animation-play-state: paused; }
.tile { flex: none; width: 9rem; background: var(--color-white); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-radius: .875rem; padding: 1rem; box-shadow: 0 14px 28px -24px rgba(30,20,80,.4); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; aspect-ratio: 1/1; transition: transform .16s ease, box-shadow .16s ease, border-color .16s ease; }
.tile:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 20px 34px -22px rgba(60,40,150,.4); border-color: var(--color-blue); }
.tile img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: contain; border-radius: .375rem; }
@keyframes marquee { from { transform: translateX(0); } to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }
.marks-note { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: .78rem; color: var(--color-muted); text-align: center; }
@media (max-width: 920px) { .marks-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.75rem; } .owner-frame { max-width: 22rem; margin: 0 auto; } }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .owner-frame::after { display: none; } }
@media (max-width: 560px) { .tile { width: 7rem; } }
</style>
